headline: Autodesk (ADSK) Seen Outgrowing Its End Markets, Rothschild Rates Buy
summary: Autodesk, Inc. (NASDAQ:ADSK) ranks among the 10 best new stocks to buy in Ray Dalio’s portfolio. On January 9, Rothschild analysts initiated coverage of Autodesk, Inc. (NASDAQ:ADSK) with a Buy rating and a $375 price target, stating that the company is on track to grow more rapidly than its end markets and recent projections suggest. […]
